## What happens at each failure type

```text
Malformed JSON arrives:
  Consumer throws JsonParseException
  ErrorHandler sees it's NotRetryable → SKIPS retries
  Sends to order.events.DLT immediately
  DLT consumer saves to dlq_messages table
  Slack alert: "Malformed JSON at offset 12345"
  Engineer fixes data, calls POST /admin/dlq/replay/456

DB temporarily unavailable:
  Consumer throws DatabaseUnavailableException
  ErrorHandler: retry attempt 1 (wait 1s)
  Retry attempt 2 (wait 2s)
  Retry attempt 3 (wait 4s)
  DB is back → attempt 2 succeeds → processed successfully
  No DLT entry

DB still down after 3 retries:
  All 3 attempts fail
  ErrorHandler sends to order.events.DLT
  Auto-replay when DB recovers
```

